data.description: This is a great deal in memorial.  The most popular floor plan in Hudson Oaks and all that is needed is some cosmetic work.  Recent new service panel, new lower cabinets in kitchen, nice flooring downstairs installed with extra for renovations or repairs.  This home is priced way under market and just needs some cosmetic  attention.  A/C working well.  If you like to pick your flooring and paint come take a look at this one.  Unit comes with 2 side by side parking spots and that is feet away from your door.   The townhouse sits in section 1b which is meticulously maintained and has a strong financial operating budget.
